{"tid":1840241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[封印高鐵] 高鐵不封 ! 港人必亡 ! 封印高鐵 !  香港封關 !","createTime":"2020-01-24T18:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T02:05:32.000Z","uid":198990,"like":78,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"79f4db9a941f6b177fa105e6042ea80c46e3662c","tid":1840241,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:26:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>特殊行動  <span style=\"color: red;\">封印</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">高鐵</span> </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MvhZUFb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMvhZUFb.jpg&h=6dd89f3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/53oN3yB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F53oN3yB.jpg&h=aafc5755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VVCK5MW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVVCK5MW.jpg&h=6f687007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目標 : 只有一個 封印高鐵 !! <br />\n時間 : 初一至初四 每日一點 !! <br />\n地點 : 西九高鐵站 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">高鐵不封 ！ </span> <span style=\"color: limegreen;\"> 港人必亡 ！</span>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[b][size=6]<span style=\"color: red;\">高鐵不封 ！ </span> <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">肺炎失控 ！</span>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">政府不封 !  </span>  <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">港人必亡 !</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">港人自救 ！ </span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">不封不散 ！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">香港封關！ </span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"> 肺炎不散 ！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高鐵如果一日<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲運作 </span></span><br />\n就代表緊每日都有成千上萬個[b]<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">武漢人同中國肺炎人可以入境播毒</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無能政府仲依然要<span style=\"color: red;\">政治大於人命</span>  連<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">拒絕武漢人入境</span>都做唔到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以一定要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[size=6]自己香港自己救</span></span></strong>! <br />\n<br />\n我地唔須要呢個<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">害我地於死地既高鐵</span></span></strong> !<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中左肺炎無藥醫 !</span> <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">肺炎傳播就會死 !</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你願意行出黎<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保護自己條命嗎?</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3eb98cffa67ea190f96cc1a6db12a1a490f5def6","tid":1840241,"uid":198990,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:26:51.000Z","msg":"其實我而家真係好驚  好驚中招 好驚死<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eNprjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eNprjS</a>"},{"pid":"5dfa066eadc96b23ef06d459d3f8c8742085f008","tid":1840241,"uid":198990,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:27:25.000Z","msg":"廢話時間<br />\n<br />\n出得行動有狗就肯定<br />\n都係個句 係咪有狗就唔出?<br />\n<br />\n依家殺到埋身 用病毒攞9你條命<br />\n你都仲側側膊唔多覺咁<br />\n再唔封印高鐵 咪等住俾人肺炎煮豬咯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好本未倒置<br />\n唔去高鐵個病源體本身有手有腳<br />\n識行識走識咳識噴口水<br />\n唔去高鐵只要佢係香港就一樣播緊毒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外唔好以為有個口罩就無事<br />\n香港班醫護有防毒geat都照中<br />\n你以為靠個醫科口罩就有用?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為呢埋係屋企無事<br />\n你唔洗番工? 唔洗搭地鐵巴士?<br />\n唔洗出街買餸?<br />\n仲記得淘大沙士事件?"},{"pid":"0e9b36149e264e87be80d42602fca143cf9acc86","tid":1840241,"uid":198990,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:28:12.000Z","msg":"封呀"},{"pid":"5e2a59b58c4497352a5b084a8160bdd892c960e8","tid":1840241,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:28:22.000Z","msg":"為自己條命行動未呀"},{"pid":"e30e978b91af10a5c284ddd9ad18af0580c1328b","tid":1840241,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:29:49.000Z","msg":"[封印高鐵] 高鐵不封 ! 港人必亡 ! 封印高鐵 !  香港封關 !<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1840241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1840241</a>"},{"pid":"f8a229bf3cb84182c7aca9aa9af50013de3fb2ed","tid":1840241,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4afbdb02404d6966f341bc98cf8916834b2195b","tid":1840241,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:29:59.000Z","msg":"[封印高鐵] 高鐵不封 ! 港人必亡 ! 封印高鐵 !  香港封關 !<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1840241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1840241</a>"},{"pid":"52cbe9a0e3b21b0527a09976f5e849edcaf5304b","tid":1840241,"uid":161025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:30:46.000Z","msg":"出黎呀香港人 唔好理有無不反啦"},{"pid":"9ddf95dfcbd8f7ab1745cac6db3a54eac3191f5e","tid":1840241,"uid":249378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:3