>\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1840241/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1840241/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"228c2fe3003986e45acaecdb3756909458135eb5","tid":1840241,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:51:03.000Z","msg":"致四大醫護專業工會<br />\n<br />\n近日致命武漢肺炎肆虐全球，世界各地的政府均已實行嚴謹的防疫措施。唯獨香港特區政府對關口的防疫工作置之不理，令大量懷疑感染新型冠狀病毒的外來患者湧入香港。<br />\n<br />\n港府在防疫工作上力度不足，以及後知後覺的態度，直接令醫護界工作壓力及感染機會大增，甚至需要以抽生死籤來決定進入隔離病房的醫護名單。在未有任何確切治療的方案下，此致命的疫症絕大機會令2003 年沙士事件中，醫護人員因受感染而死亡的傷痛事件重現，再次勾起港人的悲痛回憶。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，一眾熱心的市民已於2020年1月24日零晨，在《香港地投票》應用程式內發起了一項投票事項。投票只開放予香港境內市民，亦以一系列的措施盡力達至一人一票，其內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n議題：支唔支持醫護大罷工<br />\n投票開放時間：一個月<br />\n截至2020年1月25日零晨為止，24小時內已有1117名香港市民投票，當中約97%支持香港醫護人員罷工，約2%反對及2張廢票。<br />\n<br />\n《香港地投票》應用程式作為一個投票平台，致力為不同民生或政制議題及各種工業行動提供民意基礎。現來信各醫護工會團體，藉此轉達市民的意見。考慮到醫護人員有其專業，亦關乎病人及其家屬的權益。醫護人員罷工與否的決定將完全留待醫護界自行決定，此函只供各大機構作民意參考之用。<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票<br />\n謹啟<br />\n2020-01-25<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org%2FLetter%2F20200125.pdf&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=36cf4a72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n有勞大家幫我forword 俾醫護工會同各醫護知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"7866851959159062e696b3bd2f64af3b6d91fa3d","tid":1840241,"uid":207462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ed1321052f0008c4b2ced52d74ecfe9bcefd30","tid":1840241,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:51:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>醒下啦香港人 政府唔會救我哋 只能自救</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3c5f4f0bcf7dcff5afb9f92d4ae62dc7894ad505","tid":1840241,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:51:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42d85b460923bf85e1e246cfab7fb777205c5b02","tid":1840241,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1qB775V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1qB775V.jpg&h=a4cc2576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[封印高鐵] 高鐵不封 ! 港人必亡 ! 封印高鐵大行動 !  香港封關 ! 置頂 !<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1840241/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1840241/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"05b64b9b362aa9181c32bb19100da13ba6957800","tid":1840241,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:52:41.000Z","msg":"其實已經唔止武漢<br />\n上海等其他地方黎既人都好有機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe4e2ecce059577fa5ccaddc4dc7706eec0230d","tid":1840241,"uid":207462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b466ac1ab574117daeaf37fcf4a1fea89f5b77","tid":1840241,"uid":318928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:53:19.000Z","msg":"要快！必須要有612咁大型  已經冇退路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1840260\" data-auto-link target